---
title: Seared Steak with Spring Veggie Succotash and Mint-Chive Pesto
description: Succotash typically consists of summer’s best veggies— corn, tomatoes, peppers, and lima beans. This version takes advantage of spring asparagus and peas for a deliciously seasonal spin. A bright herb sauce wakes up the entire dish!
